description:
Dude. We are actually doing it. I just want to thank you guys for being so supportive and just joining me on this crazy adventure. YouTube full-time, let's go.

To be clear, this apartment is super cheap. An apartment just this one in Ann Arbor (where my university is) would cost around $2000 (you guys should've seen how crap the first place I looked at was, IN ANN ARBOR AT HIGHER RENT) but this one doesn't even cost half of that.

I am starting to save up to build my own PC for the occasion (getting hard to do all this with a laptop), so tips on good parts and help are much appreciated!

Once again, you've all already helped so much, this definitely isn't the beginning. We had to fight to get even here, but we're here now, and I'm loving the view. Full speed ahead.
fulltitle: A New Chapter Begins.. | NEW APARTMENT TOUR!
